---
import type { SteamAchievementPageRow } from '@/data/steam-source';
import SteamAchievementTableRow from '@/components/SteamAchievementTableRow.astro';

interface Props {
  rows: readonly SteamAchievementPageRow[];
}

const { rows } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="catalog-section steam-achievement-table-shell" aria-labelledby="steam-achievement-table-heading">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Shared payload table</p>
      <h2 id="steam-achievement-table-heading">按字段拆分的成就表</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="steam-achievement-table-note">
    表格容器支持横向滚动。键盘用户聚焦表格后，也可以继续浏览每一列的公开路径和复制动作。
  </p>

  <div class="steam-achievement-table-scroll" tabindex="0">
    <table class="steam-achievement-table">
      <caption class="sr-only">HagiCode Steam 成就目录及公开图标路径。</caption>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th scope="col">名称</th>
          <th scope="col">steamApiName</th>
          <th scope="col">localId</th>
          <th scope="col">分类</th>
          <th scope="col">奖励</th>
          <th scope="col">计划预设</th>
          <th scope="col">achieved 图标</th>
          <th scope="col">locked 图标</th>
          <th scope="col">资源动作</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody id="steam-achievement-table-body">
        {rows.map((row) => (
          <SteamAchievementTableRow row={row} />
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="empty-state steam-achievement-empty-state" data-empty-state role="status" aria-live="polite" hidden>
    <p>当前过滤条件下没有匹配的 Steam 成就。</p>
    <p>请切回“全部”分类，或尝试输入更短的 `localId`、`steamApiName`、中文名或英文名关键字。</p>
  </div>
</section>
